    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but \"letting the performance stop\" for a moment is just a temporary fix. the performance is everything. if i stop performing, there's just nothing left. it's like there's no way to actually be \"real\" again, it's just an empty space where a person used to be. if the self is gone, why keep the body around just to keep up the lie?",
